  "identifier": "HB 275",
  "title": "AN ACT relating to KEES scholarships for students attending noncertified schools.",
  "abstract": "Amend KRS 164.7874 to define \"eligible noncertified school graduate\"; amend definitions of \"KEES award,\" \"KEES award maximum,\" and \"KEES base amount\" for an eligible noncertified school graduate; amend KRS 164.7879 to establish an equivalent grade point average for eligible noncertified school graduates based on the graduate's ACT score; amend KRS 164.7881 and 164.7884 to conform.",
